LOS ANGELES COUNTY -- GOVERNMENT OFFICIALS; HISPANICS -- LOS ANGELES COUNTY; 
RACIAL DISCRIMINATION; VOTING RIGHTS; LOS ANGELES COUNTY -- SUITS; LOS ANGELES 
COUNTY -- BUDGET; POLITICAL CAMPAIGNS 
</P>
