<DOC>
<DOCNO> LA072490-0063 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 251642 </DOCID>
<DATE>
<P>
July 24, 1990, Tuesday, San Diego County Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
<SECTION>
<P>
Metro; Part B; Page 3; Column 4; Metro Desk 
</P>
