<HEADLINE>
<P>
PEOPLE 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
* James R. Liese has joined San Diego Commercial Finance as marketing manager. 
</P>
</TEXT>
<TYPE>
<P>
Column; Appointment 
</P>
</TYPE>
</DOC>
<DOC>
<DOCNO> LA072490-0079 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 251682 </DOCID>
<DATE>
<P>
July 24, 1990, Tuesday, San Diego County Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
<SECTION>
<P>
Business; Part D; Page 2B; Column 3; Financial Desk 
</P>
</SECTION>
<LENGTH>
<P>
29 words 
</P>
</LENGTH>
<HEADLINE>
<P>
PEOPLE 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
* Guy W. Winton II, corporate chairman of Winton Engineering, has been 
appointed to serve on the Building Industry Assn.'s San Diego department of 
real estate committee. 
