<P>
Brief 
</P>
</TYPE>
<SUBJECT>
<P>
CALIFORNIA HIGHWAY PATROL; TRAFFIC ACCIDENTS -- CALIFORNIA; STATISTICS; SEAT 
BELTS; AUTOMOBILE SAFETY 
</P>
</SUBJECT>
</DOC>
<DOC>
