notification of kin. Crash severely injured a 17-year-old, also of Bell, who 
was driving. Police said he would be arrested on suspicion of vehicular 
manslaughter. He was taken to Western Medical Center-Santa Ana for surgery. DON 
KELSEN / Los Angeles Times 
