<HEADLINE>
<P>
COMPUTER PROBLEMS FOUL UP STOCK OPTIONS TABLES 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
<P>
By Associated Press 
</P>
</BYLINE>
<DATELINE>
<P>
NEW YORK 
</P>
</DATELINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Computer problems at the Associated Press resulted in transmission of 
incomplete stock options tables Monday. 
</P>
<P>
A problem in computer programs that process incoming trading data resulted in 
some transactions being excluded from the tables. It could not be immediately 
determined how many transactions were missing. 
</P>
