<P>
ORANGE COUNTY -- TRANSPORTATION; ORANGE COUNTY -- ELECTIONS -- 1990; SALES TAX 
-- ORANGE COUNTY; ORANGE COUNTY TRANSPORTATION COMMISSION 
</P>
